{"tid":1914284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國：全球近3億學生因武肺停課　教育 被剝奪受教育權","createTime":"2020-03-07T12:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T13:13:38.000Z","uid":225130,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2a38d4c70a5d98f7f1a9da492286f32e1385156a","tid":1914284,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情快速擴散，在義大利昨（4日）宣布各級學校全面停課後，聯合國教科文組織（UNESCO）表示，目前全球已有近3億學生被迫失學，教育所受的影響史無前例，可能影響受教權。<br />\n<br />\n根據UNESCO的報告，目前已因武肺疫情下令全面停課的國家地區，包括中國、香港、澳門，日本、蒙古、北韓、義大利、亞美尼亞、亞塞拜然、巴林、伊朗、伊拉克、科威特、黎巴嫩、阿拉伯聯合大公國，共造成2億9千萬名兒童和青年失學。此外，美國，法國，德國，英國，南韓，新加坡，泰國，越南和巴基斯坦等9國也有部分地區學校停課。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n雖然在大型危機時暫時停課並不罕見，但UNESCO主席阿祖萊（Audrey Azoulay）表示，全球教育體系受到干擾的規模和速度都是空前的，「若持續下去，可能威脅到受教權」。　（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d848949b76a5ebe922a5e4938b8431b1ec295606","tid":1914284,"uid":7484,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"屌，多得你WHO 囉"},{"pid":"12d41e60b90bd03a614eb660eef45dba137e6df0","tid":1914284,"uid":7043,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"On9 <br />\n冇事個陣俾你上到驚都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659c20b715d8f77150e0bbeead54585881b85766","tid":1914284,"uid":50801,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"要讀書定要命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b48b51fcf786ea0c3f390de8faca1ded96dd80","tid":1914284,"uid":37596,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲要靠上堂學習？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c365e14c8555d2aa870cbdc46f21975279c5d81